# ==============================================================================
# Notes for Developers
# ==============================================================================
# Auto-created folders by the preprocessing endpoint:
# - product_images/  : Contains product images for similarity matching
# - __generated__/   : Contains preprocessed features (*.h5, *.csv, *.json)
# - uploads/         : Temporary folder for API file uploads
#
# To track product images in git, comment out the line: product_images/
# To track generated features in git (not recommended), comment out: __generated__/
# To track uploads in git (not recommended), comment out: uploads/
# To track environment files, comment out: .env
# 
# Remember to never commit:
# - API keys or secrets
# - Large binary files (use Git LFS if needed)
# - Sensitive configuration files
# - Local development settings
# - Generated ML features and preprocessed data
